 Lun7-kau3 hian7-kim e5 lang5, toa7-poaN3 si7 liah8 jin5-cheng5 khoaN3 khah tui3-tiong7, bo5 lun7 hit e5 lang5 e5 pun2-su7 si7 chaiN2-iuN7. Siat-su2 goa2 e5 siu5-jin5, tek-khak si7 kong2 in m7 ho2; ia7 na7 si7 goa2 e5 chhin-chhek, chiu7 eng7 hiah-e5 ho2 oe7 lai5 o-lo2 in; long2 m7 kheng2 kong2 kong-to7 e5 oe7. Bu2 Sam3-su bat kong2, Kap goa2 ho2 e5, chiu7-si7 ho2 lang5; kap goa2 phaiN2 e5, chiu7-si7 phaiN2 lang5; sit8-chai7 chin-chiaN3 si7 u7 iaN2. Chong2-si7 lan2 kau3-hoe7 lai7 e5 lang5 iau3-kin2 m7-thang chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni; tioh8 oh8 Ki5 Hong5-iong5 chiau3 kong-to7 chiah ho2. U7 si5 in2-chin3 lang5 lai5 jip8 seng3-kau3, a2 si7 ku2-chian3 lang5 lai5 thak8 Toa7-oh8, long2 tioh8 chiau3 hit e5 lang5 e5 phin2-heng7 chim-chiok lai5 kong2; m7-thang u7 chit8-tiam2-a2 phian-than2 e5 sim. In-ui7 lan2 sou2 in2-chin3 ku2-chian3 e5 lang5, na7 choe3-liau2 u7 ho2 bou5-iuN7, chiu7 lan2 ia7 u7 eng5-kng. Siat-su2 sou2 chian3 e5 lang5, in e5 sou2 choe3 long2 bo5 chiau3 lan2 ku2-chian3 hit si5 e5 oe7, a2-si7 kau3 poaN3-tiong-tng5 chiah taN2-chha3, chiu7 lan2 ku2-chian3 e5 lang5 ia7 chin phaiN2 se3-bin7; boe7 bian2-tit hou7 lang5 kong2 lan2 si7 bo5 chiau3 kong-to7, a2-si7 kong2 lan2 boe7 bat lang5. Sou2-i2 kou2-cha2 e5 hoat-tou7, na7 ku2-chian3-tioh8 gau5 lang5, ko2-jian5 u7 li7-ek ti7 kok-ka, chiu7 po2-ku2 e5 lang5 ia7 tit-tioh8 siuN2-su3; iah8 na7 chian3 m7 tioh8 lang5, choe3-liau2 m7 ho2 u7 hoan7-choe7, hit e5 po2-ku2 e5 lang5 ia7 tioh8 lian5-cho7. Chhin-chhiuN7 chit-tiap8 e5 po2-cheng3-jin5 tioh8 lian5-tai3 in e5 chek-seng5 hit khoan2. Kho2-kian3 teh chian3 lang5 e5 koan-he7 si7 chin toa7, m7-thang sui5-pian7 hut-liok8 i . 
 Chha5 koe u7 oan5-choan5 e5 tek-heng7 
 Ki2 Seng2-chu2 teh ka7 Chiu Soan-ong5 chhi7 hit ho7 sio-phah koe; i2-keng ka3 ke3 chap8 jit8 ku2, Soan-ong5 mng7 kong2, Chit chiah koe oe7 eng7 tit hou7 i sio phah a2 boe7? Ki2 Seng2-chu2 kong2, Chit chiah koe iau2-koh si7 chin kiau-ngou7, gau5 sai2 seng3-te7, boe7 oe7 eng7 tit hou7 i kap pat8 chiah sio-phah tit. Au7-lai5 koh ke3 chap8-jit8, Soan-ong5 koh mng7 i kong2, Chit chiah koe oe7 hou7 i sio phah tit a2 boe7? Ki2 Seng2-chu2 kong2, Chit chiah koe iau2-koh si7 na7 thiaN-kiN3 sim2-mih8 hiang2, i chiu7 thi5, a2-si7 khoaN3-tioh8 sim2-mih8 iaN2, i chiu7 jip; iau2-be7 thang kap pat8 chiah sio-phah tit. Iu7-koh ke3 chap8 jit8, Soan-ong5 iu5-goan5 teh mng7, Ki2 Seng2-chu2 kong2, Iau2 si7 boe7 eng7 tit, in-ui7 na7 teh khoaN3 sim2-mih8, iu5-goan5 chin chhiN-kong5, ia7 gau5 siu7-khi3; sou2-i2 boe7 eng7 tit. Bak8-chit8-nih iu7 ke3 chap8 jit8, Soan-ong5 iu7 koh chiau3 cheng5 an2-ni mng7, Ki2 Seng2-chu2 chiah kong2, Chha-put-to oe7 eng7-tit hou7 i khi3 sio-phah tit lah. Sui-jian5 u7 pat8 chiah koe teh thi5, i khiok na2-chun2 bo5 thiaN-kiN3, chu7-chu7 chai7-chai7, put-tong7 seng-sek, khoaN3-liau2 chhin-chhiuN7 chha5 e5 koe; sou2-i2 tek-heng7 sng3 si7 chiau5-pi7, pat8 chiah-e5 koe khoaN3-tioh8 i, boe7 bian2-tit ka-ki7 to3-the3 tui3 au7-bin7 khi3 liau2. 
 Chi-na2 Tiong5-kang hit si3, na7 kong2 lang5 e5 pun2-su7 bo5 cheng-kong, u7 chit8 ku3 siok8-gu2 kong2, PoaN3 pan5 chhou3. Tai7-khai3 si7 kong2, Chhou3 toe2 poaN3-pan5 na7-tiaN7, sio2-khoa2 chit8-e7 io5 chiu7 u7 siaN; na7 toe2 kau3 tiN7 lai5 ka7 i io5, chiu7 bo5 thiaN-kiN3. Chhin-chhiuN7 hit ho7 bat chit8-hang7 poaN3-hang7, sio2-khoa2 u7 to7-hak8 e5 lang5, i chiu7 chin kiau-ngou7 chu7-ko, na7 kap lang5 choe3 tui, chiu7 phin2 i e5 pun2-su7. Siat-su2 si7 chin-chiaN3 to7-hak8 khah koaiN5, tek-heng7 chin ho2, hak8-bun7 ia7 chhim hit khoan2 e5 lang5, in chiu7 hoan2-tng2 chin khiam-pi. Leng7-goa7 u7 chit8 khoan2, beng5-beng5 si7 u7, khoaN3-liau2 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 bo5, beng5-beng5 si7 chat8-chat8, khoaN3-liau2 na2-chun2 khang-khang e5 heng5-chong7. Siok8-gu2 u7 kong2, Chin chiong-kun put-chai7 ti7 jiong5 chong. Ia7 kong2, U7--e5 m7 kong2, bo5--e5 teh phin2-phong2, chiu7-si7 chit e5 i3-su3. 
 M7 chai ka-ki7 u7 piN7 
 Pian2 Chhiok si7 Tiong-kok kou2-cha2 e5 si5, choe3 u7 mia5-siaN e5 i-seng. U7 chit8 jit8 tui3 Che5-kok keng-ke3, jip8-khi3 kiN3 Che5 Hoan5-kong, Pian2 Chhiok chiu7 ka7 Hoan5-kong kong2, Kun-hou5 e5 phe5-hu hian7-si5 u7 piN7 teh; na7 bo5 i-ti7, chiu7 oe7 ju2 chhim. Hoan5-kong kong2, Goa2 to bo5 piN7. Ke3 gou7 jit8 au7, Pian2 Chhiok koh kiN3-tioh8 Hoan5-kong, iu7 ka7 i kong2, Kun-hou5 e5 piN7 i2-keng kau3 ti7 tng5 ui7 e5 sou2-chai7; na7 m7 i-ti7, oe7 ti3 khah chhim. Hoan5-kong ia7 bo5 in3 i. Kau3 Pian2 Chhiok chhut khi3, Hoan5-kong put-chi2 m7 hoaN-hi2, tui3 kun-sui5 i e5 lang5 kong2, He2, choe3 i-seng e5 lang5, ai3 than3 lang5 e5 chiN5, beh tian2 in e5 pun2-su7; goa2 beng5-beng5 to bo5 sim2-mih8 m7 ho2, i ia7 kong2 goa2 u7 piN7. Koh ke3 gou7 jit8, Pian2 Chhiok iu7 lai5 kiN3 Hoan5-kong, chit8-e7 khoaN3-tioh8, chiu7 oat8-tng2-sin choe3 i chhut-khi3. Hoan5-kong chiu7 kio3 lang5 khi3 mng7 i, khoaN3 si7 chaiN2-iuN7. Pian2 Chhiok chiu7 kong2, PiN7 ti7 phe5-hu, eng7 ioh8 lai5 soe2, a2 si7 eng7 he2 lai5 ku3, chiu7 oe7 i tit. PiN7 ti7 huih-meh8, eng7 chu3-sia7 ia7 oe7 i tit. Na7 piN7 ti7 tng5-ui7 e5 sou2-chai7, eng7 ka, eng7 chiu2 e5 ioh8-lui7 ia7 koan2 oe7 tioh8. PiN7 kau3 ti7 kut-chhe2, sui-jian5 si7 chip-chiang2 siN-si2 e5 koan5-peng3, ia7 bo5 hoat-tou7 liau2. Hian7-si5 kun e5 piN7 i2-keng jip8 ti7 kut-chhe2; goa2 sou2-i2 m7 kaN2 koh kong2 sim2-mih8. Au7-lai5 koh ke3 gou7 jit8, Che5 Hoan5-kong hut-jian5 khi2 piN7, kio3 lang5 khi3 tiau3 Pian2 Chhiok; Pian2 Chhiok i2-keng choe3 i to5-siam2. Ke3 bo5 joa7 ku2, Hoan5-kong chiu7 piN7 si2. 
 Hian7-si5 choe7-choe7 hit khoan2 ui5-hui chok-tai2 e5 lang5, peng5-sou3 ia7 u7 hit ho7 ho2 e5 chhin-chiaN5 peng5-iu2 khou2-khng3 in, in khiok long2 m7 thiaN; kau3 au7-lai5 hou7 koaN-hu2 liah8 khi3 heng5-hoat8 teng7 choe7, chiah chai thang siuN7-tioh8 bou2 lang5 sou2 kong2 e5 oe7 si7 tioh8, chong2-si7 i2-keng bo5 lou7-eng7 liau2. Koh chhin-chhiuN7 chit-tiap8 e5 Thoan5-tou7 sian-siN teh kong2 to7-li2, kin-a2-jit8 kio3 lang5 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3, bin5-a2-chai3 ia7 si7 kio3 lang5 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3, m7-ku2 se3-siok8 lang5 long2 m7 kheng2 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3, koh m7 sin3 ka-ki7 u7 choe7. Kau3 au7-lai5 u7 chit8 jit8 khia7 ti7 sim2-phoaN3 tai5 cheng5, Siong7-te3 mng7 choe7 e5 si5-chun7, hit-tiap8 beh hoan2-hoe2, khiok si7 siuN ban7 lah. 
