 Chhou2 kok u7 chit8 e5 tiau5-tit8 e5 lang5, in lau7-pe7 thau-khan lang5 e5 iuN5, i chau2-khi3 kong-tng5 chhut siu2. KoaN-hu2 liah8 in lau7-pe7 lai5, in-ui7 i e5 kiaN2 choe3 kan-cheng3, bo5 oe7 thang chiN3, chiu7 teng7-choe7 beh thai5 i. Chit e5 tiau5-tit8 e5 lang5 iu7 chhiaN2 koaN-hu2 pang3 i e5 lau7-pe7, i kam-goan7 thoe3 i e5 lau7-pe7 si2. Au7-lai5 kau3 teh-beh thai5 e5 si5-chun7, chit e5 lang5 tui3 hiah-e5 ge5-iah8 kong2, Goan2 lau7-pe7 thau-khan lang5 e5 iuN5, goa2 khi3 tng koaN chhut siu3, an2-ni goa2 kiam2 m7 si7 chit8 e5 tiau5-tit8 koh sin3-sit8 e5 lang5 mah? Goan2 lau7-pe7 hoan7-choe7 tioh8 thai5, goa2 kam-goan7 thoe3 i si2, an2-ni goa2 kiam2 m7 si7 chit8 e5 hau3-chu2 mah? Chhin-chhiuN7 goa2 chit khoan2 e5 sin3-sit8 koh u7 hau3 e5 lang5, keng3-jian5 tioh8 hou7 lang5 thai5, chit kok lai7 iau2 u7 sim2-mih8 lang5 m7 tioh8 thai5 leh? Chhou2 ong5 thiaN-kiN3 chiah-e5 oe7, chiu7 sia3-bian2 hit e5 lang5 bo5 thai5. Khong2-chu2 thiaN-kiN3 chiah kong2, Chin ki5-koai3 ah, u7 chit khoan2 e5 tiau5-tit8 lang5, sng3 choe3 si7 u7 sin3-sit8, keng3-jian5 eng7 in lau7-pe7 lai5 boe2 ho2 mia5-siaN hou7 lang5 o-lo2, chin-chiaN3 si7 ki5-koai3. 
 Na7 lun7 se3-kan, eng2-eng2 u7 chit8 khoan2 e5 lang5, peng5-siong5-si5 mih8-iuN7 kan-khiau2 to u7, eng7 pah poaN khui2-khiat e5 ke3-bou5; na7 khoaN3-kiN3 bou2-mih8 lang5 khah gu5-chhun2, chiu7 beh khi3 khi-hu7 i, khoaN3-kiN3 sim2-mih8 lang5 khah loan2-jiok8, chiu7 beh khi3 hai7 i, long2 bo5 chit8 tiam2-a2 jin5-ai3 e5 sim-chiaN5, ia7 bo5 chit8 tiam2-a2 lin5-bin2 e5 cheng5-i3. Kip8-chi3 kau3 au7-lai5, khi-hu7 lang5 ia7 khi-hu7 kau3 chiok lah, hai7 lang5 ia7 hai7 kau3 chin7 liau2, put-gi7 e5 chiN5-chai5 ia7 eng7 long2 boe7 liau2. Hit-si5 khiok siuN7 beh chhe7 chit8 e5 ho2 lang5 e5 mia5 lai5 choe3; chiu7 khi3 siu-li2 chit8 tiau5 kio5, a2 si7 khi3 cheng2-li2 chit8 keng bio7, sang3 lang5 kui2 nia2 mi5-hiu5, a2-si7 hoat tam7-poh8 bi2 hou7 song3-hiong lang5, chiu7 giam2-jian5 ka-ki7 liah8 choe3 ho2 lang5 teh choe3 ho2 su7. Chiau3 an2-ni khoaN3, in na7 beh chhin-chhiuN7 chit khoan2 e5 teh kiu5 ho2 lang5 e5 mia5-siaN, put-ju5 cha2-jit8 boh8-tit choe3 hit ho7 hai7 lang5 e5 tai7-chi3 kiam2 m7 si7 koh khah ho2 mah? 
 Hoan2-hoe2 jin7 choe7 
 Chhit kok e5 si5, Lin7 Siong-ju5 sng3 si7 ho2 khau2-chai5, koh u7 tam2-lek8 e5 lang5, i u7 oan5-choan5 hit te3 po2-gek8 to3-lai5 Tio7-kok, ia7 ti7 Bin2-ti5 e5 sou2-chai7, bo5 leng5-jiok8-tioh8 i e5 kun-ong5. Sou2-i2 Tio7-ong5 hong i choe3 siong7-kheng. Chit-ui7 tian-to3 pi2 Liam5 Pho2 khah koaiN5. Liam5 Pho2 chit8-e7 siuN7, Goa2 tui3 siau3-lian5 kau3 taN, keng-ke3 kang2 pah pai2 e5 cheng-chian3, chiah choe3 chiong-kun e5 chit; Lin7 Siong-ju5 put-ko3 kho3 i e5 khau2-chai5, hoan2-tng2 pi2 goa2 koaN choe3 khah koaiN5. Chiu7 tui3 lang5 kong2, Goa2 na7 tu2-tioh8 Siong-ju5 e5 si5, tek-khak beh leng5-jiok8 i. Siong-ju5 thiaN-kiN3 chit ho7 oe7, mui2 pai2 chhut-lai5 e5 si5-chun7, na7 khoaN3-kiN3 Liam5 Pho2, chiu7 koaN2-kin2 siam2 tui3 piN-a2 khi3. I sou2 eng7 e5 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 in chu2-lang5 chit ho7 khoan2, chiu7 liah8-choe3 toa7-toa7 e5 kian3-siau3; tai7-ke lai5 tui3 Siong-ju5 saN-si5, beh khi3 pat8 ui7. Siong-ju5 chiah ka7 in kong2, Hian7-si5 te7-it kiong5 te7-it toa7 e5 chiu7 si7 Chin5-kok. Chong2-si7 goa2 ti7 i tian7-teng2, siong7-chhiaN2 kaN2 toa7 siaN hoah lai5 chek-pi7 i Chin5 ong5, ho5-hong3 Liam5 Chiong-kun, goa2 kiam2 chin-chiaN3 si7 teh kiaN mah? Put-ko3 chit-tiap8 Chin5-kok m7 kaN2 lai5 phah Tio7-kok, chiu7-si7 in-ui7 u7 goan2 nng7 lang5, na7 kau-chiap ong2-lai5 e5 su7, goa2 oe7 siat-hoat, m7-ku2 cheng-chian3 e5 tai7-chi3, iu5-goan5 tioh8 kho3 Liam5 Chiong-kun. Siat-su2 goan2 nng7 e5 put-ho5, si7 chhin-chhiuN7 nng7 chiah hou2 teh saN-chiN, hit e5 se3-bin7 oh-tit long2 oah8; sou2-i2 goa2 na7 kiN3-tioh8 i, chiu7 tai7-seng siam2-pi7. In-ui7 goa2 si7 liah8 kok-ka e5 tai7-chi3 choe3 khah iau3-kin2, i tui3 goa2 sng3 si7 ko3-jin5 e5 hiap8-hiam5 na7-tiaN7, sou2-i2 bo5 beh kap i ke3-kau3 lah. I sou2 eng7 e5 lang5, thiaN-liau2 put-chi2 u7 cheng5-li2, ia7 chiu7 oh8 in chu2-lang5 e5 khoan2, tu2-tioh8 Liam5 Pho2 e5 kun-lang5, ia7 long2 khah niu7 i. Liam5 Pho2 hit peng5 e5 lang5, chiu7 na2 kiau-ngou7 khi2 lai5, liah8 choe3 Siong-ju5 chin-chiaN3 kiaN i. Au7-lai5 u7 chit8 lang5 mia5 kio3 Gu5 Kheng, lai5 chhe7 Liam5 Pho2, chiong Lin7 Siong-ju5 e5 i3-su3 thiah beng5 hou7 i thiaN. Liam5 Pho2 chiah chhiN2-gou7 hoan2-hoe2, chiu7 thng3-pak-theh pe7 chit8 ki tek-poe, lai5 Siong-ju5 in tau jin7 choe7, chhiaN2 Siong-ju5 eng7 tek-poe chek-hoat8 i. Siong-ju5 chin hoaN-hi2 khan i e5 chhiu2, chhiaN2 i jip8-khi3 lai7-bin7, ho2 le2 khoan2-thai7 i; nng7 lang5 soa3 kiat choe3 siN-si2 e5 kau-poe5. 
 Lun7-kau3 put-ho5 e5 tai7-chi3, m7-na7 kok-nih8 u7 an2-ni, ke-lai7 ia7 si7 u7 an2-ni. Chiu7-si7 Ia5-sou e5 kau3-hoe7, ia7 boe7 kong2 tit chiu7 bo5 an2-ni. Bat khoaN3-kiN3 u7 si5 chit peng5 e5 kau3-hoe7 khoaN3-khin hit peng5 e5 kau3-hoe7, a2 si7 hit peng5 e5 hoe7-iu2 khoaN3-khin chit peng5 e5 hoe7-iu2. U7 si5 kong2 bou2 lang5 si7 kiu5 piaN2 tit-tioh8 piaN2, a2 si7 kong2 bou2 lang5 si7 oa2-kho3 se3-lek8, ia7 bat kong2 bou2-mih8 lang5 to bo5 hak8-bun7, hoan2-tng2 teh choe3 chip-su7, a2 si7 kong2 bou2 mih8 lang5 to bo5 jiat8-sim, chaiN2-iuN7 teh choe3 thoan5-to7. An2-ni tai7-ke phoe-pheng5; kong2-liau2 to long2 u7 in e5 li2-khi3. Su7-put-ti Mou5-kui2 i2-keng than3 chit e5 ki-hoe7, hou7 li2 li7-khui cheng3-keng e5 lou7, lai5 jip8 ti7 i e5 khoan-tho3 lah. Ia7 chiu7-si7 se3-siok8 lang5, in-ui7 khoaN3-kiN3 lan2 e5 hoe7-iu2 ka-ki7 put-bok8, bo5 saN-thiaN3 e5 sim, oe7 soa3 kiaN kau3 m7 kaN2 lai5; an2-ni kau3-hoe7 thai3 oe7 heng-ong7 nih? Sou2-i2 chhim-chhim ng3-bang7 kau3-hoe7 lai7 e5 peng5-iu2, na7 u7 chit ho7, chiu7 koaN2-kin2 koe2; na7 bo5, ia7 tioh8 kin2-sin7 m7-thang hoan7-tioh8, boh8-tit u7 phang7 thang hou7 Mou5-kui2 jip8-khi3. 
